FROM node:18-alpine
WORKDIR /app
COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm ci --only=production
COPY student-app.js .
EXPOSE 9393
USER node
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
  CMD wget --no-verbose --tries=1 --spider http://localhost:9393/api/health || exit 1
CMD ["node", "student-app.js"]